com.github.bordertech.wcomponents

Class WProgressBar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.AbstractWComponent
      • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.WBeanComponent
        • com.github.bordertech.wcomponents.WProgressBar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AjaxTarget, BeanAware, BeanBound, BeanProviderBound, DataBound, Labelable, WComponent, WebComponent, Serializable

    public class WProgressBar
extends WBeanComponent
implements AjaxTarget, Labelable

    WProgressBar is a component for displaying progress bars. The number of steps in the progress bar is configurable, and the progress bar's value can either be set manually, or sourced from an Integer bean.

    Methods are available to customise the progress bar's appearance, such as setting its size or whether to display the progress as a fraction or percentage.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Yiannis Paschalidis
